title: Holy Cow
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Set in old Khmer style house decorated with local art, above road down to ochateal and serendity. Around 1/2 of the menu items are veg: cottage pie, tofu sandwich on handmade bread, vegan curry, amok with tofu, pasta, jacket potatoes, and vegan chocolate cake. Garden setting, has Wi-Fi and laundry service on site.
